## Relationship to other comment rules

| Rule | Use for |
|------|---------|
| **This rule** | **Class role** — who owns what in the design |
| [stomp4j-in-code-documentation.mdc](stomp4j-in-code-documentation.mdc) | **Method/block** — spec detail, rejected alternatives, non-obvious invariants |
| Public API Javadoc | Parameters, return values, `@throws` on exported methods |

Do not duplicate the class block inside methods. Do not restate the block in markdown unless updating ARCHITECTURE.md module boundaries.

## Agent checklist (new or changed type)

1. Add or update the responsibility block before finishing.
2. **Doing** lists at least one concrete verb.
3. **Not responsible for** names at least one neighbour (factory, template, protocol layer, test assertion, etc.).
4. If the type is user-visible capability, confirm [features.md](../../docs/features.md) / guides still accurate — see [documentation.mdc](documentation.mdc).

